title: Hour 2 - Dr. Jerry Jones Diagnoses Dak, Aidan Hutchinson
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Dr. Jerry Jones Diagnoses Dak, Aidan Hutchinson
description:
Dan gets a chuckle out of Dallas Cowboys Owner, Jerry Jones diagnosing QB Dak Prescott's injury and shaving weeks off of his expected recovery timetable. And he talks to Detroit Lions Rookie DE, Aidan Hutchinson about spending his rookie training camp on 'Hard Knocks.'
